drop table "CON_RObject" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "CON_RObject" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_RObject"
(
"RObjectID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ContractID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"SAPContractCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"CompanyCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"EntityCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"ObjectType" VARCHAR2(10) not null,
"RSCode" VARCHAR2(100) not null,
"ObjecGroupName" VARCHAR2(60),
"GroupCode" VARCHAR2(10) default '0010',
"InforAssgin" VARCHAR2(10),
"ReserObjType" VARCHAR2(10),
"ObjectStartDate" TIMESTAMP,
"ObjectEndDate" TIMESTAMP,
"ObjectFrom" TIMESTAMP,
"ObjectTo" TIMESTAMP,
"ChangeIndicator" CHAR(1) default 'N' not null,
"SyncSAPflag" INTEGER default 0 not null,
constraint PK_CON_ROBJECT primary key ("RObjectID")
);

comment on column "CON_RObject"."ObjectType" is
'IL或IM';

comment on column "CON_RObject"."RSCode" is
'对应SAP的CONTRACT_OBJECT_ID';

comment on column "CON_RObject"."ObjecGroupName" is
'如为IL，对应展位编号';

comment on column "CON_RObject"."GroupCode" is
'对应SAP的OBJECT_GROUP_NUMBER，';

comment on column "CON_RObject"."InforAssgin" is
'对应SAP的INFORMATIONAL_ASSIGNMENT';

comment on column "CON_RObject"."ReserObjType" is
'对应SAP的RESERVATION_OBJ_TYPE';

comment on column "CON_RObject"."ObjectStartDate" is
'对应SAP的POSSESSION_FROM
';

comment on column "CON_RObject"."ObjectEndDate" is
'对应SAP的POSSESSION_TO';

comment on column "CON_RObject"."ObjectFrom" is
'对应SAP的OBJECT_VALID_FROM';

comment on column "CON_RObject"."ObjectTo" is
'对应SAP的OBJECT_VALID_TO';

comment on column "CON_RObject"."ChangeIndicator" is
'N:初始创建
I:新增
D:删除';
